                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius Naso <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>tesserar</abbr><ex>iarum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>in Asia <expan><abbr>nav</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Γάϊος Ἰούλιος Νά<lb break="no" n="2"/>σων ὁ ἐπὶ τῶν τεσ<lb break="no" n="3"/>σαραρίων ἐν Ἀσίᾳ <lb n="4"/>πλοίων
            </ab></div></div>
